				<td colspan="2"><span>NP, but this info is pepperd throughout dozens of threads here.
<br />

<br />
/stopsong
<br />
/cast 1
<br />

<br />
That stops your song and stars another one. That's how you twist songs with macros. Don't multicast in macros it is not a good idea for bards.
<br />

<br />
Sinfonian</span></td>
