				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Macro Madness  =P<a name="19008"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 4 04 9:56 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I use these socials for songs 1-6 (which I hit with my left hand on home row):
<br />

<br />
/stop
<br />
/cast #
<br />

<br />
For 7 I usually have either an Incoming Message or a pet attack hotkey.  The 8th spot I just have the 8th song (speed or invis indoors) which I can tap to stop playing.
<br />

<br />
It's half the keypresses, that's all.
<br />

<br />
When I'm chant kiting I use GameVoice to loop a 4-twist because it's so boring.  In a group I manually twist, and when 2-boxxing with my monk then I use GameVoice and add &quot;/assist Sorikk&quot; to the socials and leave Limry on autofollow.  It's like a poor man's shaman.</span></td>
