				<td colspan="2"><span>If memory serves me right it was very easy.. The interface for it was simple to use. You could get it to hit hotkeys or type /cast 1.. Timing was done in milliseconds and was easy.. The only real down side to it was if you had lag your macro's wouldn't work right.. But for the most part they were dead on.. You might even be able to find a pre-built one for EQ from another Bard..
<br />

<br />
Either way it wont take you more then a half hour to set one up.. And now that you can get out of EQ without quitting it should be easier..</span></td>
