<br />

<br />
5.) Is there anyway to break the macro during the delay.  It seems if I break a macro at the right time it takes a lot of time before it responds again.
<br />

<br />
Could someone post their macro so I can compare notes. 
<br />

<br />
Any help would be great...  (I am 4 deaths in the hole atm.. because of the caps lock issue... I am a slow learner I guess)</span></td>
